GNU Typist  is an interactive typing  tutor that can help  you to type
correctly.  It has  several lessons for different keyboards  layouts and in
different languages.   The lessons  for typist are  described in  a easy
scripting language that  the user can use to  modify the exising lessons
or create new ones.

